overview: Five men and women deal with the absurdity of finding and coming to terms with love in the big city in this at times raunchy film. Micah doesn't understand why his boyfriend won't come out of the closet in a city as liberal as New York City. Jess' days of chasing after men come to an end after finding the right one, while thirty-something Leia can't quite exorcise the ghosts of lover's past. David tries to maintain a long-distance relationship while fighting for his dreams. And Alejandro's spiritual search is curtailed by his partner's sexual cravings.
title: It's a Match
